{"tid":2026675,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"元朗黃店連日被毀 疑犯逃脫","createTime":"2020-05-21T06:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T06:14:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e27c83f0e4c3a4d1270877210e89cf226e5cb9","tid":2026675,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:14:24.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200521/B6N6JRHQOJ57AT6JFOFPD7NNCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2FB6N6JRHQOJ57AT6JFOFPD7NNCU%2F&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsX0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=85ebd88c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2FB6N6JRHQOJ57AT6JFOFPD7NNCU%2F&h=a57bd118\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200521/B6N6JRHQOJ57AT6JFOFPD7NNCU/</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗黃店連日被毀 疑犯逃脫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589992001_291c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589992001_291c.jpg&h=7ce15069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n豪記蔬果檔如常開業，並繼續貼有支持抗爭的標語。 張家豪攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】元朗民主派議員辦事處及黃店，過去一周接連遭到刑事毀壞，其中位於安寧路的黃店豪記蔬果，昨凌晨被四至六名男女在鐵閘噴上「反骨仔」塗鴉，再撕走文宣貼及換上辱罵泛民的單張，居住樓上的東主發現追截，惟對方人多勢眾，只能目送逞兇者逃去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCCTV錄低撕文宣噴塗鴉<br />\n<br />\n根據豪記蔬果提供的CCTV片段顯示，<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n兇徒最終在對面大廈後巷失去蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589992001_4baa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589992001_4baa.jpg&h=e5d7a19e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩名女子撕走紙張及用噴漆塗污店面。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶，該店本周一凌晨時分，亦遭一名戴口罩的男子撕走店外文宣，未知兩次事件是否同一班人所為。<br />\n<br />\n上周四元朗區區議員黎國泳水邊辦事處及石景澄大橋路辦事處，凌晨4時許不約而同<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n至於該名女疑犯是否與破壞豪記蔬果的兇徒屬同一幫人仍待調查。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張家豪"}]}